column1: #Text=Dai Li sergeant says : " You are the property of the Earth Kingdom .
#Text=" Dai Li sergeant says : " Never show mercy !
#Text=Now attack your opponent , and this time , like you mean it !
#Text=" Dai Li sergeant says : " A soldier never apologizes to his enemy !
#Text=" Kai says : " I 'm not a soldier !
#Text=" Dai Li sergeant says : " You will be when I 'm through with you .
